title: Hour 1: Operation BBQ Relief
description:
Witty was fun at a party, the Mets may have lost due to a cheating scandal, and Tom Brady is seeing a lot of bad football. Plus, we speak to Bryan Mroczka of Operation BBQ Relief about the devastation he's seen on the West Coast of Florida due to Hurricane Ian and what they are doing to help. To donate, visit worldofsuey.com/ian-relief.
